description: This skill gives out a random machine learning approach, varying from decision trees to clustering. The content from this skill comes from the Wikipedia page on "Machine Learning." There are thirteen different approaches it can tell you about.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask machine learning approaches for a machine learning fact.
Alexa, ask machine learning approaches to tell me a fact.
Alexa, ask machine learning approaches to give me a machine learning trivia.
name: Machine Learning Approaches
shortDescription: Give random machine learning approaches from Wikipedia
